<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-016-244 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 444 660</DOCID><JOURNAL>Computergram International  Nov 4 1991 n1797* Full Text COPYRIGHT Apt Data Services (UK) 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Other financings. (Comdisco Inc. receives financing) (BriefArticle)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   Comdisco Inc. (Finance).andO;Ticker:    CDO.andO;Topic:     FinancingCredit.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>OTHER FINANCINGSandM;Comdisco Inc, Rosemont, Illinois has reached two new financing arrangementswith its group of worldwide commercial banks worth $685m.andP;  The agreementsconsists of a $375m multi-option facility coordinated by National WestminsterBank Plc, with 10 additional lenders, and a $310m global agreement withAlgemene Bank Nederland NV and Westpac Banking Corp with eight additionallenders.andP;  The facilities include provision for letter of credit-enhancedcommercial paper programmes of up to $525m and the total effect is to provideliquidity in all currencies for both domestic and European subsidiaries,bringing its total committed facilities to more than $800m.andP;  Proceeds of anydrawings will be used for working capital funding, debt management, andcontinued expansion into related business lines.andO;</TEXT></DOC>